## Three-Layer Verification Method

| Layer | Name | What It Checks | Tools |
|-------|------|---------------|-------|
| 1 | Existence | Does the artifact exist? | `ls`, `grep` for exports |
| 2 | Substantiveness | Is it more than a stub? | `wc -l`, grep for implementation |
| 3 | Wiring | Is it connected to the system? | `grep` for imports/usage |

